{"word":"G3858 - παραδέχομαι - paradéchomai - par-ad-ekh'-om-ahee - Receive","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραδέχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paradéchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ad-ekh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Receive</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஏற்றுக்கொள், சேர்த்துக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":"1. to receive, to take up, to take upon oneself"},{"paragraph":"2. to admit to accept"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1209 - δέχομαι - déchomai - dekh'-om-ahee/1209\">G1209</a>; to <i>accept near</i>, that is, <i>admit</i> or (by implication) <i>delight</i> in: - receive.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}